{"id": "1417128605590491207", "channel_id": "1417128605590491207", "type": 0, "author_id": "134247328876986369", "author_name": "aegisx", "author_bot": false, "content": "● The Awakener \"Ryker\" gains a new effect for the talent \"Soulforge Aptitude\": the Black Sigils Ryker acquires increase by 40%~80%.\nThis one only apply to his Talent \" Winner Take All \"  and it still hard for ppl get 500 Sigil if doing stage with mob have high att and a lot hp", "timestamp": "2025-09-15T12:43:08.549000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-09-15T12:44:31.348000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "Clown", "emoji_id": "1400771541423226971", "count": 5}, {"emoji": "🤮", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1417128605590491207", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」About new Ryker buff", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785", "1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1417189059406856295", "channel_id": "1417189059406856295", "type": 0, "author_id": "218840371084525568", "author_name": "eternalis_era", "author_bot": false, "content": "Hello,\nI don't know if this is a bug, a mistranslation or just me that don't understood correctly.\nHowever Pickman Chromaphage card say \"if inspiration is triggered gain 2 additional instances of damage\" \nSo for me if I use inspiration twice during the turn (Rouse + Exalt), the instances of damage should go up to 7 but it's locked to 5.\nPlus, the translation between the in fight card and the awaken tab card is different which make it really misleading. (see screenshot)\nOn one side you understand that the + damage instance will carry over turn but on the other side you're not even sure. Well it doesn't carry anyway and I don't mind it, but I suppose this part is more about mistranslation and I should mention it.\n\nAlso, the name \"Fantasia\" whenever you use his Rouse or trigger exalt with 10 creativity is named \"Frenzy\" on character buff list.", "timestamp": "2025-09-15T16:43:21.862000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1417189060031676426", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 395514, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1417189059406856295/1417189060031676426/image.png?ex=69ff642a&is=69fe12aa&hm=dc715680ef5e0d3ef47fa47dcd8cb6e1ca2c89669fe20ee3d19b732f7108a6ec&"}, {"id": "1417189060526735431", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 506730, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1417189059406856295/1417189060526735431/image.png?ex=69ff642a&is=69fe12aa&hm=d9c7b26ccc80543888f2eee74445876c3d30bd8cabd74edb683c346bd4e8c2eb&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1417189059406856295", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「Processing」Pickman - Chromaphage \"inspiration\"", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785", "1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1417197507741487207", "channel_id": "1417197507741487207", "type": 0, "author_id": "735137568307282011", "author_name": "reya.li", "author_bot": false, "content": "Hi,\nEarlier in the day I did a low score Deep Dive run as a test to check the boss' HP. Later that same day I did a 72000 point run successfully, but the server doesn't seem to have registered it properly even about an hour later since it's still counting Deep Dive Scholar and the old score. <:dead:1356082627509092372>  You can see the clear in this video as well. \nhttps://youtu.be/diSIlqXoBtM\n您好，\n今天稍早時，我進行了一次低分深潛探勘（Deep Dive）作為測試，以確認首領的血量。同一天稍晚，我成功完成了一次72000分的挑戰，但即使過了一個多小時，伺服器似乎仍未正確記錄這次成績——目前仍顯示著「深潛學者」的舊分數。您也可以在此影片中看到此次通關記錄。", "timestamp": "2025-09-15T17:16:56.102000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "takenotes", "emoji_id": "1357186646294138890", "count": 6}, {"emoji": "cry3", "emoji_id": "1356082134447558748", "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1417197508458971256", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2061548, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1417197507741487207/1417197508458971256/image.png?ex=69ff6c08&is=69fe1a88&hm=d0b8b926abad962ccb35e6ea8905939bf9ab870d9fd87ac7383458b1bc1395c0&"}, {"id": "1417197508970680391", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1795315, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1417197507741487207/1417197508970680391/image.png?ex=69ff6c08&is=69fe1a88&hm=3d1cfde7f3c4ba5118a8ebcdfc536b125294a693b0916579c2af791b00d5f054&"}, {"id": "1417197509444632727", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1034665, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1417197507741487207/1417197509444632727/image.png?ex=69ff6c08&is=69fe1a88&hm=89bce79c710d4fddbe80640d70db85e445cfb1776c0dc946ad8dd310558287b3&"}], "embeds": [{"type": "video", "title": "Morimens 忘卻前夜 - 72000 Deep Dive vs. Leigh - Uvhash 3m+ Dmg", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=diSIlqXoBtM", "description": "I tried to do commentary but my mic settings weren't right, still you can kind of hear that I was enthused by the hit!"}], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1417197507741487207", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Not Crediting Highest Score/Rank in Deep Dive", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1417225669880057998", "channel_id": "1417225669880057998", "type": 0, "author_id": "478214049033879563", "author_name": "yannic2112", "author_bot": false, "content": "When thinking about what to upgrade, it helps to see what bonuses the next level provides, be that for units‘s cards or for Wheels‘s effects. Currently, you can only tap on „Next“ once to see what the next level gives you. I suggest adding the ability to be able to see what you get for all level ups (could be by being able to click the „Next“ button multiple times) to help with choices on what you want to invest in.\nFor example, do I want to increase the level of a certain card for a unit or will that card give me overall worse stats for my investment than another card would? Should I even level that one to begin with or does it make more sense to, idk level the exalt or something. Do I want to go for copies of a certain SSR wheel or are the effects not good enough? \nSuch questions arise when you try to plan around your limited resources and such a feature would help a lot with that.", "timestamp": "2025-09-15T19:08:50.479000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "☝️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}, {"emoji": "Meow", "emoji_id": "1400771520757891123", "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1417225669880057998", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Add ability to see all card levels", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
