{"id": "1417189146044403813", "channel_id": "1417189146044403813", "type": 0, "author_id": "1403431686116741143", "author_name": "2300011747", "author_bot": false, "content": "打完深潜以后没有头衔，应该是出bug了，请尽快修复。如果因为此bug影响了深潜的每日奖励请给出补偿。", "timestamp": "2025-09-15T16:43:42.518000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1417189146044403813", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」UID100562628打完深潜18000后没有头衔", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1417104509536043079", "channel_id": "1417104509536043079", "type": 0, "author_id": "233874560682950656", "author_name": "wolfierce", "author_bot": false, "content": "Hello,\nWith the help of the community I tried to find out the formula that outputs the final stats of the relics and orisons in the game, since one of the Pickman's skill depends on it, but, alas, it's harder than I would have thought.\n\nAt best, I can say that it scales much faster toward the last 10 levels, it caps at 70, perhaps it doesn't increase at every levels but at some intervals, and at least the number of posses increases the final stats on last step of the formula.\n\nBut I'll give in and ask directly, is it possible to have details about how it scales based on levels and number of posse? The only ingame maths we have is that each posse increases the final stats by 1%, up to a max of 50%.", "timestamp": "2025-09-15T11:07:23.602000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1417104509536043079", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Stats formula of the relics/orisons", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785"]}
{"id": "1416940904534769734", "channel_id": "1416940904534769734", "type": 0, "author_id": "693983290423509042", "author_name": "climbkaly", "author_bot": false, "content": "There were a few people in chat that asked for help with the Ultra level in the summer event.\n\nI was going to create a video to help them. But when I looked at the team.....who chose the covenants for it? Do they even play Ultra?????\n\nI've attached the original team with abysmal choices for covenants. And my suggested covenants. \n\nIf you repeat this event again next year, could you please change the covenants to actual useful ones? \n\nThanks.", "timestamp": "2025-09-15T00:17:17.130000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1416940904966787093", "filename": "Better.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1125364, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1416940904534769734/1416940904966787093/Better.jpg?ex=69ff25cd&is=69fdd44d&hm=3c10c50c8bacc3875f4ea3c768497a4471f1b41cbc8a004fa2f3b80523341e99&"}, {"id": "1416940905717305394", "filename": "Original_team.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1196151, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1416940904534769734/1416940905717305394/Original_team.jpg?ex=69ff25cd&is=69fdd44d&hm=5a79e1bc025d878818f7c02d72f0760cceba95e9945f4be0005baa191b5c8d8d&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1416940904534769734", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Change Covenants - Summer Event Ultra Team", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785"]}
